L,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('376457','Primal Vigor','C13','Enchantment','R','{4}{G}','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If one or more tokens would be created, twice that many of those tokens are created instead.£If one or more +1/+1 counters would be put on a creature, twice that many +1/+1 counters are put on that creature instead.',NULL,NULL,'Matt Stewart','162','3.714','£10/17/2013: It doesn’t matter who controls the tokens or the creature that the +1/+1 counters are being placed on.£10/17/2013: Primal Vigor affects permanents that “enter the battlefield with” a certain number of counters. For example, if a creature would normally enter the battlefield with three +1/+1 counters on it, it will enter with six +1/+1 counters on it.£10/17/2013: If there are two Primal Vigors on the battlefield, the number of tokens or +1/+1 counters is four times the original number. If there are three on the battlefield, the number of tokens or +1/+1 counters is eight times the original number, and so on.','G',NULL,'14.25','19.99','25.19',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'G',NULL,NULL,'Vigueur primordiale','Urkraft des Lebens','Vigore Primordiale','野生の活力',NULL,NULL,'Vigor primitivo',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Enchantement','Verzauberung','Incantesimo','エンチャント',NULL,NULL,'Encantamiento',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Si au moins un jeton devait être mis sur le champ de bataille, mettez deux fois ce nombre de jetons sur le champ de bataille à la place.Si au moins un marqueur +1/+1 devait être placé sur une créature, placez deux fois ce nombre de marqueurs +1/+1 sur cette créature à la place.','Falls ein oder mehrere Spielsteine ins Spiel gebracht würden, werden stattdessen doppelt so viele dieser Spielsteine ins Spiel gebracht.Falls eine oder mehrere +1/+1-Marken auf eine Kreatur gelegt würden, werden stattdessen doppelt so viele +1/+1-Marken auf sie gelegt.','Se una o più pedine stanno per essere messe sul campo di battaglia, invece ne vengono messe il doppio.Se uno o più segnalini +1/+1 stanno per essere messi su una creatura, invece ne vengono messi il doppio.','１個以上のトークンが戦場に出る場合、代わりにその２倍の数のトークンを戦場に出す。クリーチャーの上に＋１/＋１カウンターが１個以上置かれる場合、代わりにその２倍の数の＋１/＋１カウンターをそのクリーチャーの上に置く。',NULL,NULL,'Si fueran a ponerse una o más fichas en el campo de batalla, en vez de eso, se pone en el campo de batalla el doble de esas fichas.Si fueran a ponerse uno o más contadores +1/+1 sobre una criatura, en vez de eso, se pone el doble de esa cantidad de contadores +1/+1 sobre esa criatura.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('376458','Pristine Talisman','C13','Artifact','C','{3}','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'{T}: Add {C}. You gain 1 life.','#_"Tools and artisans can be destroyed, but the act of creation is inviolate."—Elspeth Tirel_#',NULL,'Matt Cavotta','255','3.053','£6/1/2011: Pristine Talisman has a mana ability. Its ability doesn’t use the stack and can’t be responded to.','A','{C}','0.09','0.2','0.95',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Talisman immaculé','Makelloser Talisman','Talismano Integro','清純のタリスマン',NULL,NULL,'Talismán prístino',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Artefact','Artefakt','Artefatto','アーティファクト',NULL,NULL,'Artefacto',NULL,NULL,NULL,'{T} : Ajoutez {1} à votre réserve. Vous gagnez 1 point de vie.','{T}: Erhöhe deinen Manavorrat um {1}. Du erhältst 1 Lebenspunkt dazu.','{T}: Aggiungi {1} alla tua riserva di mana.£Guadagni 1 punto vita.','{T}：あなたのマナ・プールに{1}を加える。あなたは1点のライフを得る。',NULL,NULL,'{T}: Agrega {1} a tu reserva de maná. Ganas 1 vida.',NULL,NULL,NULL,'#_« Les outils et les artisans peuvent être détruits, mais l''acte de création reste pur. »—Elspeth Tirel_#','#_„Werkzeuge und Handwerker können zerstört werden, aber der Akt des Erschaffens bleibt unberührt."—Elspeth Tirel_#','#_"Gli attrezzi e gli artigiani possono essere distrutti, ma l''atto della creazione è inviolato."—Elspeth Tirel_#','#_「道具や職人は失われます。だけど、創造の行いは犯されません。」――エルズペス・ティレル_#',NULL,NULL,'#_"Las herramientas y artesanos pueden ser destruidos, pero el acto de creación es inviolable".—Elspeth Tirel_#',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('376459','Propaganda','C13','Enchantment','U','{2}{U}','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Creatures can''t attack you unless their controller pays {2} for each creature they control that''s attacking you.','#_"The cost of your opposition will be extracted from your wits."—Nekusar, the Mindrazer_#',NULL,'Clint Cearley','53','4.367','£10/4/2004: The payment is made during the declare attackers step at the same time you are declaring the attacker.£10/4/2004: If there is more than one Propaganda on the battlefield, the cost is cumulative.£10/4/2004: If there are multiple attacks in a turn, then you have to pay for each attack.£10/4/2004: Paying this cost is not an instant or any other kind of ability, it is an additional cost on the declaration of the attacker.£2/1/2007: In the Two-Headed Giant format, you still only have to pay once per creature.£2/1/2014: Unless some effect explicitly says otherwise, a creature that can’t attack you can still attack a planeswalker you control.','U',NULL,'4.99','6.1','7.99',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'U',NULL,NULL,'Propagande','Propaganda','Propaganda','プロパガンダ',NULL,NULL,'Propaganda',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Enchantement','Verzauberung','Incantesimo','エンチャント',NULL,NULL,'Encantamiento',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Les créatures ne peuvent pas vous attaquer à moins que leur contrôleur ne paie {2} pour chaque créature qu''il contrôle qui vous attaque.','Kreaturen können dich nicht angreifen, falls ihr Beherrscher nicht für jede dich angreifende Kreatur, die er kontrolliert, {2} bezahlt.','Le creature non possono attaccarti a meno che il loro controllore non paghi {2} per ogni creatura che controlla che ti sta attaccando.','クリーチャーは、そのコントローラーが、自分がコントロールするあなたを攻撃しているクリーチャー１体につき{2}を支払わないかぎり、あなたを攻撃できない。',NULL,NULL,'Las criaturas no pueden atacarte a menos que su controlador pague {2} por cada criatura que controle que te está atacando.',NULL,NULL,NUL